    <body>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abstract:&lt;/strong&gt; &quot;One cable to rule them all&amp;rdquo;. I intend to build a system where all the basic peripherals - keyboard, mouse and display, can be connected to BeagleBone by attaching it with a USB cable to Android phone. This will be implemented as a kernel module and an ready to use out-of-box app for Android. This module shall have a greater reach and also serve as seed for extending to other systems - Windows, iOS, Ubuntu phones etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Tools:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;All these details can be found at&amp;nbsp;http://elinux.org/BeagleBoard/GSoC/BARD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Codebase:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Available on github with seperate repositories for Kernel driver and Android application.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Kernel driver code:&amp;nbsp;https://github.com/praveendath92/bard-linux&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Android app code:&amp;nbsp;https://github.com/praveendath92/bard-droid&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Progress tracking:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #333333; font-family: &apos;Helvetica Neue&apos;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.399999618530273px;&quot;&gt;Through weekly reports posted on&amp;nbsp;https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/beagleboard-gsoc/FvT9XR3P5Ow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</body>
